_2_1_1754556963442_16910\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">住宅作品／Photo Credit：創喜設計 JCPC DESIGN</span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">創喜設計今年七歲了。聊到未來，甄嬉瞇著眼笑說：「我很期待我要出唱片欸！」語氣輕鬆得像在說「等一下去吃午餐」，讓現場的人都笑了出來。<br><br>「我相信，那些來到我面前的事情，如果我願意接住它、好好地做完，它就會變成我生命的一部分。」對甄嬉而言，無論是設計還是生活，都是靠著日復一日的投入與堅持，慢慢累積出屬於自己的樣子，就像她一貫的溫柔哲學──專注當下、相信過程，用「創造喜樂」的心，穩定前行。</p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1754556963442_16910 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"